Usage: reportFreqViolation [-help] [-detailed] [-em_type {avg peak rms all}]
                           [-excInstFile <string>] [-outfile <string>]
                           [-reportFormat <integer>] [-selInstFile <string>]
                           [-slew {min max}]
                           [-sort {name freq minDiff maxDiff minFreq maxFreq}]
                           [-tableScale <float>] [-view <string>]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-detailed                        # Report detail info (bool, optional)
-em_type {avg peak rms all}      # Specify the EM type(Default:avg)
                                 # (enum, optional)
-excInstFile <string>            # Excluded instance file name
                                 # (string, optional)
-outfile <string>                # Output report file name
                                 # (Def.=freqViolations.rpt) (string, optional)
-reportFormat <integer>          # Specify the format of the report (Def.=0)
                                 # (int, optional, min=0, max=2)
-selInstFile <string>            # Selected instance file name
                                 # (string, optional)
-slew {min max}                  # Specify the slew used for the report
                                 # (Def.=min) (enum, optional)
-sort {name freq minDiff maxDiff minFreq maxFreq}
                                 # Specify the sorting type for the report (enum, optional)
-tableScale <float>              # Scale factor for EM table value (Def.=1.0)
                                 # (float, optional)
-view <string>                   # Active view name (string, optional)